WEBVTT

00:00:01.274 --> 00:00:06.690
Kakva je buducnost ucenja?

00:00:06.690 --> 00:00:08.970
Ja imam plan,

00:00:08.970 --> 00:00:12.050
ali kako bih vam objasnio kakav je plan,

00:00:12.050 --> 00:00:15.020
moram vam ispricati malu pricu,

00:00:15.020 --> 00:00:17.866
kako bih vam ga docarao.

00:00:17.866 --> 00:00:19.653
Pokusao sam pronaci

00:00:19.653 --> 00:00:23.060
koje je porijeklo danasnjeg skolovanja,

00:00:23.060 --> 00:00:25.330
odakle je poteklo?

00:00:25.330 --> 00:00:27.762
Mozemo se vratiti daleko u proslost,

00:00:27.762 --> 00:00:31.575
ali ako pogledamo danasnje skolovanje kakvo jeste,